Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.28,0:00:13.97,JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,人生の幸　不幸
Dialogue: 5,0:00:15.01,0:00:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If everything is already set in stone by fate,
