Dialogue: 5,0:00:20.02,0:00:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,then why are we even born?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.07,0:00:22.57,JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,俺達は何のために生まれてくるのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.97,0:00:33.82,JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,裕福な家庭に生まれる人
Dialogue: 5,0:00:31.99,0:00:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,There are those born wealthy,
