Dialogue: 5,0:00:37.65,0:00:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and those born into war or poverty.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.84,0:00:40.56,JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,飢餓や戦争の真っ只中に生まれる人
Dialogue: 5,0:00:42.32,0:00:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's all caused by fate, then God must be incredibly unfair and cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.33,0:00:44.90,JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それらが全て　運命だとすれば
