Dialogue: 5,0:23:27.70,0:23:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.96,0:23:31.73,JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,俺はこの体の全てを焼き尽くしても
Dialogue: 5,0:23:28.99,0:23:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if my body was to burn to ashes,
Dialogue: 5,0:23:32.05,0:23:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't give up on you.
